Package: lifeviz
Title: A Shiny App to visualize life events
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Matias",
           family = "Andina",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "matiasandina@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: The goal of lifeviz is to visualize life events. This has been inspired by the post The Tail End by WaitButWhy. I have taken the visualizations and added a few degrees of freedom, so that the users can visualize past/present, as well as any activity they could represent using emojis.
